### Logging / GUI - other

*   [Logary (‚≠ê527)](https://github.com/logary/logary) - Logary is a high performance, multi-target logging, metric, tracing and health-check library for Mono and .NET. .NET's answer to DropWizard. Supports many targets, built for micro-services.

*   [ALGLIB](https://www.alglib.net/) - ALGLIB is a cross-platform numerical analysis and data processing library. It supports several programming languages (C++, C#, Delphi) and several operating systems (Windows and POSIX, including Linux) **\[Proprietary]** and **\[Free Edition]**

### Misc / GUI - other
